# RapidAid QR Medical Profile UI Design

## Purpose

The QR Medical Profile allows first responders and hospitals to instantly access a patient's critical medical information by scanning a secure QR code during an emergency.

## Page Layout

### Header

- 🚑 RapidAid Logo
- Dashboard
- QR Profile
- Notifications
- Profile

## QR Profile Section

### QR Code Card

Display:

- QR Code
- Patient Name
- Unique QR ID
- Last Updated Date

Buttons:

- Download QR
- Share QR
- Print QR
- Regenerate QR

---

## Personal Information

Display:

- Full Name
- Date of Birth
- Age
- Gender
- Blood Group

---

## Medical Information

Display:

- Allergies
- Existing Medical Conditions
- Current Medications
- Disabilities (if any)
- Organ Donor Status

---

## Emergency Contacts

Display:

- Contact Name
- Relationship
- Mobile Number

Support multiple emergency contacts.

---

## Insurance Details

Display:

- Insurance Provider
- Policy Number
- Valid Until

---

## Hospital Preferences

Display:

- Preferred Hospital
- Preferred Doctor
- Preferred Language

---

## Security & Privacy

Features:

- Secure QR Generation
- Encrypted Medical Data
- Scan Access Logging
- Patient Consent Management

---

## Quick Actions

- Edit Medical Profile
- Update Emergency Contacts
- Update Insurance Details
- Download Medical Summary

---

